data.description: Welcome to Eagles Pointe, a highly sought-after neighborhood where luxury living meets practical convenience.  This stunning colonial home spans three finished levels and is loaded with extra storage throughout and boasts a new HVAC system (circa 2020) featuring electronic zoning and twin Nest thermostats.  The top two levels encompass over 3000 sqft of meticulously designed living space.  As you enter the main level, you are greeted by an office, library and separate dining and living rooms.  The kitchen is a chef's dream with beautiful cherry cabinets, granite countertops, and upgraded black stainless steel appliances.  The main level features amazing hardwood floors that add a touch of elegance to the entire space.  Step outside to a maintenance-free Trex deck that offers a peaceful retreat  into a fully fenced yard, overlooking wooded surroundings.  The spacious owners suite is a true retreat, complete with a custom closet for organization enthusiasts.   The convenience of a renovated laundry room on the same level adds a practical touch to everyday living.  Nestled between Quantico and Fort Belvoir, this property is situated in a prime location.  With great storage options and a desirable living experience, this home in Eagles Pointe is a perfect blend of comfort and luxury.
